<HEADLINE>
<P>
CLIPPERS' HANDLING OF KIMBLE IS TYPICAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Once again the Clippers have demonstrated that nothing has changed and that 
they will remain a second-class organization into the 1990s. 
</P>
<P>
The Clippers land Bo Kimble, a bona fide player and a marketing dream, then 
allow their attorney to belittle him in public. Very intelligent. 
</P>
<P>
TERRENCE J. SCHAFER 
</P>
<P>
Huntington Beach 
