<DOCNO> LA101390-0030 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 291712 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 13, 1990, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 15; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
114 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH JANICE; 
</P>
<P>
THE REMATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Franny Frizzle fizzled out in Friday's seventh race costing me a mythical 
