before halftime. The extra-point attempt was blocked by Eugene Dreher, who also 
blocked a field-goal attempt in the first quarter. Antelope Valley (1-5, 0-1) 
took a 7-6 lead late in the third quarter on a seven-yard Fossati run. Blanks' 
interception of a Jay Mapson pass started the drive at the Palmdale 36-yard 
