<DOCNO> LA101390-0071 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 291813 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 13, 1990, Saturday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 11B; Column 3; Sports Desk 
</P>
